{
  "texts": [
    "They show that familiarity of dialect improves the quality of the models trained on such a dataset.",
    "As a result, representations that capture dialects have been used for sentiment analysis.",
    "Mdhaffar et al. [2017] present models based on SVM and multi-layer perceptron (MLP).",
    "Mulki et al. [2019] use a syntax-ignorant n-gram composition to create embeddings.",
    "The classifier model is a dense neural network that works on the addition of word embeddings, with a softmax at the end."
  ]
}